At 02:02 PM 5/29/00 +0800, you wrote:
>Hi Friends:
>To my knowledge, DMDX supports only 2 buttons-response to gain the 
>Response Time. Other 3 buttons are for other aims. How to get RT by 4 buttons?

   With <mpr>, <mnr> and <mr> you can use any number of keys.  Combined 
with <zor> and it's kin and a few macros DMDX's input is about as flexible 
as I could imagine making it.  You can implement rating scales, typed word 
input and changing correct one of many responses from item to item.


